msgid "All done?"
msgstr "¿Todo listo?"

msgctxt "116_Officer"
msgid "You only managed to arrest one of them? Well, I suppose it's better than nothing."
msgstr "¿Solo atrapaste a uno? Pues, supongo que es mejor que nada."

msgctxt "128_Officer"
msgid "We took care of the other two."
msgstr "Ya nos hicimos cargo de los otros dos."

msgctxt "140_Officer"
msgid "This is a little something to thank you for your help."
msgstr "Esto es un pequeño detalle para agradecerte por tu ayuda."

